data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Calhoun School District! This newer split level home boasts a perfect blend of modern comfort and convenience, offering an ideal lifestyle for you and your family. Situated on a level lot, this property invites you to experience spacious living with an emphasis on versatility. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by expansive, light-filled rooms designed for both relaxation and entertaining. The large flex space on the lower level in this home provide endless possibilities - transform them into a home office, a playroom, or a cozy media room to suit your lifestyle. The spacious deck overlooks the backyard that is ready for your personal touchCothink play areas, gardens, or anything you envision. The location ensures that you're never far from the essentials. Enjoy the convenience of being just moments away from shopping centers, top-rated schools, and an array of restaurants. Need medical care? The hospital is conveniently close, providing peace of mind for you and your loved ones. Commute with ease as this home offers quick access to the interstate, making your daily travels a breeze. And when it's time for leisure, the charm of downtown is just a short drive away, offering entertainment and a vibrant community atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home. Schedule your showing today and experience the best that this desirable location has to offer! USDA 100% financing eligible.
